eshmun.decisionprocedure

Class TableauNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • eshmun.decisionprocedure.TableauNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AndNode, OrNode

    public abstract class TableauNode
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class that represents node in the tableau, the node could either be an AndNode or an OrNode.

    A node contains a list of incoming and outgoing edges, as well as a formula (AbstractExpression).

    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    Mouhamad Sakr, Kinan Dak Al Bab
